Chromosomal stability in buccal cells was linked to age but not affected by 
exercise and nutrients - Vienna Active Ageing Study (VAAS), a randomized 
controlled trial.

Franzke B(1), Schober-Halper B(2), Hofmann M(2), Oesen S(2), Tosevska A(3), 
Nersesyan A(4), Knasmüller S(4), Strasser EM(5), Wallner M(6), Wessner B(7), 
